config.page.advancements.description: Advancements are well- you know what they are. These in particular can help you track your progress and give you something fun to look forward to while he's haunting you.
config.page.burning_base.description: You're lost in dark again. You head for the warm orange light that your home emits through the brush, but something is off. It's too bright, too intense, it's on fire. As you sprint towards your decaying shelter only one thought runs through your mind: "I'm on singleplayer."
config.page.chilled_candles.description: "What a cozy library." you think as you explore. You begin to light the candles scattered throughout as you explore the halls, teaming with books. That's when it happens. The room is now pitch black and all you can make out in the darkness are two white eyes staring back at you.
config.page.crimson_curse.description: You pass over the hill to your villager farm, as your head begans to peak over the various levels of blocks you notice something off. "Redstone?" you ask outloud. Entering the farm, you descend the stairs and look up. The glowing eyes help you forget about your torches.
config.page.disappearing_torches.descrip: Something is off. You've been thinking about it since you got back from mining but can't quite put your finger on it. This thought weighs on your mind like an anvil. As the night approaches you realize, your torches are missing. You didn't break them.
config.page.dreadful_donation.descriptio: Crap, garbage, and junk. Your chests of full of it. You've been putting it off but you finally decide to sort through your mess. While sorting, you notice things. Strange things. Items that aren't yours and renamed torches. He's been waiting for you to find them.
config.page.fearful_footsteps.descriptio: It's getting dark and you can't find your way back. You come across a clearing and check your coordinates. That's when you hear it, the patter of feeting moving quickly to your left, then to your right. They're too fast to be a mob, and now they are rapidly approaching from behind. Run.
config.page.ghost_doors.description: You had just got back from a long mining trip. Tired and weary you put your iron in your furnace, time slows as you wait for it to smelt. That's when you hear it, your base's door opening behind you. You're in singleplayer. Don't turn around.
config.page.ghost_miner.description: You've been alone in this cave for what feels like hours. You decide it's time to leave so you begin to strip mine up. Block by block you get closer to the surface, but your ears must be decieving you. There's no way you heard that. There it is again. You dig to your right...
config.page.haunted_herd.description: You finished rounding up the sheep with your dog, but you notice one has wandered away. You follow its noises into the thicket. Your dog does not approach. He hides behind your legs. The sheep stares unblinking, as though, for a moment, it saw you through different eyes.
config.page.leafless_grove.description: You stumble through the dark forest, strugging to see forward through the dense leaves. Just one hundred blocks away and that's when you notice it. You can see your base clear as day from way farther than usual. All the leaves are gone, and there is no lava pit to be seen.
config.page.lights_out.description: This page allows users to control integrated settings from our other project Lights Out! Step into the darkness with Lights Out, a Minecraft resourcepack/datapack that makes the dark even darker.
config.page.malevolent_shrine.descriptio: Herobrine's shrine is a classic Herobrine structure that you can build to provoke him. Building one of these shrines is an easy way to initiate Herobrine's eerie activities without waiting for the default 3 day timer.
config.page.sightings.description: You walk slowly through the dense fog after having just punched your first couple trees. You come across a clearing, a chicken emerges from the brush but it doesn't grab your attention. The figure watching you from the fog does...
config.page.sinister_signs.description: You start your recording excited to continue your survival let's play. Your torches were disappearing and they wouldn't stop, so you'd started using glowstone. As you approach your house you notice something in front of your door. It's a sign that reads: "Nice glowstone. It's mine now."
config.page.skin_library.description: The Skin Library offers a variety of Herobrine appearances for use during sightings. You can choose a specific skin to suit their preference or let the mod randomly select one for added unpredictability. This customization enhances the eerie atmosphere and keeps encounters fresh and unique.
config.page.structures.description: This field feels like it goes on forever. "Just a little farther.." you tell yourself as your eyes open and close, your finger resting on the W key. "Just gotta get home then I can- What is that?" you mumble in your zombified state. Glowstone doesn't spawn in the overworld...
config.page.twisted_tapestries.descripti: You wake in the night, and scan your room like usual, comforted by the paintings on the walls. You're barely off to sleep when thunder jolts you up. Scanning again, its dark, the paintings seemingly different. Lightning strikes and reveals them now staring right back with pale irises.
config.page.vanishing_delay.description: The Vanishing Delay setting allows you to adjust how long Herobrine lingers after a sighting. This ensures that even those who might have trouble noticing him can still experience his unsettling presence.
config.setting.advancements.description: Changes whether or not you will get advancements. (Disabling this clears your progress.)
config.setting.biome_boards.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will change the type of sign he places based on the wood around him.
config.setting.burning_base.description: Herobrine will try to burn your house down once you leave the area. (One check every 5 minutes.)
config.setting.burning_base_chance.descr: Changes the chance that Herobrine will successfully burn down your house.
config.setting.caution_caption.descripti: When the shrine is activated Herobrine will slip you a spooky message into your subtitles.
config.setting.chilled_candles.descripti: Herobrine will douse the flames on your candles when you're not around. (One check every 5 minutes.)
config.setting.chilled_candles_chance.de: Changes the chance that Herobrine will douse the flames on your candles.
config.setting.creeping_sighting.descrip: Spawns standing behind you waiting for you to turn around.
Changes how long it takes for Herobrine to disappear after being caught creeping up on you.
config.setting.crimson_curse.description: Herobrine will replace torches with redstone ones and lanterns with soul ones. (One check every 5 minutes.)
config.setting.crimson_curse_chance.desc: Changes the chance that Herobrine will execute Crimson Curse.
config.setting.disappearing_torches.desc: Herobrine will try to break your torches once you leave the area. (One check every 5 minutes.)
config.setting.disappearing_torches_chan: Changes the chance that Herobrine will successfully break your torches.
config.setting.dreadful_donation.descrip: Changes whether or not Herobrine will leave you gifts in your chests. (One check every 5 minutes)
Changes the chance that Herobrine will successfully leave you gifts.
config.setting.dwelling_shadow.descripti: If a dwelling Herobrine spawns in the dark, he will refuse to disappear while in the darkness.
config.setting.dwelling_sighting.descrip: Spawns watching you just out of view from the darkest corners of your caves.
Changes how long it takes for Herobrine to disappear after being caught dwelling in a cave.
config.setting.eerie_entrance.descriptio: Changes whether or not a joined game message will display at the end of the haunting delay.
config.setting.emissive_layers.descripti: Changes whether or not certain parts of the Herobrine skins will glow.
config.setting.fearful_footsteps.descrip: You will hear hear disembodied footsteps around you. (One check every 5 minutes.)
Changes the chance that you will hear disembodied footsteps around you.
config.setting.flickering_flashlight.des: When Herobrine is nearby he can make your flashlight flicker. [EPILEPSY WARNING!]
config.setting.ghost_doors.description: Herobrine will sometimes open and close your doors. (One check every 5 minutes.)
config.setting.ghost_doors_chance.descri: Changes the chance that Herobrine will successfully open and close your doors.
config.setting.ghost_miner.description: Herobrine will mine tunnels around you in strip mines and on the surface. (One check every 5 minutes.)
config.setting.ghost_miner_chance.descri: Changes the chance that Herobrine will dig tunnels in your world.
config.setting.give_him_control.descript: This will give him full control over the config.
config.setting.give_him_control_alt.desc: This will give me full control over the config.
config.setting.haunted_heirlooms.descrip: Changes whether or not Herobrine will leave you custom paintings and music discs when donating.
config.setting.haunted_herd.description: Herobrine may possess common passive mobs to help him better blend into his environment.
config.setting.haunted_herd_chance.descr: Changes the chance that Herobrine will successfully possess a passive mob.
config.setting.haunting_delay.descriptio: Changes the delay for how long it takes for Herobrine to start major haunting (in-game days).
config.setting.leafless_grove.descriptio: Herobrine will remove the leaves from forests that you've visited. (One check every 5 minutes.)
config.setting.leafless_grove_chance.des: Changes the chance that Herobrine will remove leaves from forests that you've visited.
config.setting.letter.description: When enabled, Herobrine will place large glowstone letters in the plains and deserts of your world.
config.setting.lurking_language.descript: Changes the language that Herobrine communicates in. (Used when he places signs or leaves donations.)
config.setting.lurking_sighting.descript: Spawns lurking around you watching from a very far distance.
config.setting.lurking_vanishing_delay.d: Changes how long it takes for Herobrine to disappear after being caught lurking around you.
config.setting.malicious_malfunction.des: Causes the game to crash on jumpscare. [EPILEPSY WARNING!] [NOT FOR WEAKER MACHINES!]
config.setting.mossy_pyramid.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will place mossy pyramids in the forests of your world.
config.setting.nametag.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine has a nametag and how it appears.
config.setting.nightmare_sighting.descri: Appears at the foot of your bed when you sleep, watching.
config.setting.no_sleep.description: Makes Herobrine prevent you from sleeping when he's nearby. (Will not work on peaceful.)
config.setting.rekindling_shrine.descrip: Changes whether or not Herobrine will relight doused shrines if you walk away for too long.
config.setting.sand_pyramid.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will place sand pyramids in the deserts and beaches of your world.
config.setting.shrine_strike.description: Changes whether or not lightning strikes when activating a Herobrine shrine.
config.setting.shrine_surprise.descripti: Changes whether or not Herobrine will appear on top of your shrine when lit.
config.setting.shrouded_specter.descript: Changes what particles appear when Herobrine disappears.
config.setting.sighting_frequency.descri: Adjusts the frequency of Herobrine appearing. (Spawn rate doubles at night.)
config.setting.sighting_noise.descriptio: Changes whether or not a noise is played when you spot Herobrine. (50% chance.)
config.setting.sighting_sense.descriptio: Changes whether or not your pet wolf will sense when Herobrine is nearby.
config.setting.sighting_sense_chance.des: Changes the chance that wolves will notice Herobrine's presence.
config.setting.sinister_signs.descriptio: Changes whether or not Herobrine will place signs with ominous messages.
config.setting.sinister_signs_chance.des: Changes the chance that Herobrine will place signs during different events.
config.setting.sneaky_strike.description: Herobrine will try to hit you if you take too long to notice him during a dwelling or creeping sighting.
config.setting.sneaky_strike_chance.desc: Changes the chance that Herobrine will hit you when you take too long to notice him.
config.setting.soul_shift.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will replace your lanterns when executing Crimson Curse.
config.setting.stalking_sighting.descrip: Spawns standing anywhere around you stalking you from a distance.
Changes how long it takes for Herobrine to disappear after being caught stalking you.
config.setting.sudden_scare.description: Enables the ability for Herobrine to jumpscare you when you collide with him.
config.setting.suspenseful_sighting.desc: Changes whether or not Herobrine will play a suspense strike when spotted.
config.setting.twisted_tapestries.descri: Herobrine will try to change your paintings to haunted versions. (One check every 5 minutes.)
config.setting.twisted_tapestries_chance: Changes the chance that Herobrine will successfully haunt your paintings.
config.setting.window_watcher.descriptio: Toggles whether or not Herobrine will continue watching you when spotted through a window.
config.setting.wooden_cross.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will place wooden crosses in the forests of your world.
